{"title":"霞光","authors":["毛岸青邵华"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":11,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪念杨开慧烈士诞辰一百周年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛岸青邵华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是云彩飘在天上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是彩霞映红湘江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长夜逝去黎明归，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你仍是美丽端庄的霞姑娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨花似雪的季节里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骄杨挺立在绿野上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清新宜人的晨光中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你回到了故乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，骄杨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，霞姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们爱你那片最美的霞光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们崇敬那棵宁折不弯的骄杨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：杨开慧的小名叫霞，乡亲们称她为霞姑。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}